item.title: CVE-2016-2169|2024-09-16T18:44:03.609Z -- cloud%20foundry -- cloud%20controller
item.description: Cloud Foundry Cloud Controller, capi-release versions prior to 1.0.0 and cf-release versions prior to v237, contain a business logic flaw. An application developer may create an application with a route that conflicts with a platform service route and receive traffic intended for the service.
